description:
Add new API endpoints and enhance existing ones to provide richer convoy data.

## New Endpoints
- GET /convoys/:id/detail - Full convoy with all tracked issue details, workers, synthesis status
- GET /convoys/stranded - Find stranded convoys (ready work, no workers)
- POST /convoys/:id/close - Manual close with reason
- GET /synthesis/:id/status - Synthesis readiness check

## Enhanced Data Types
```typescript
interface ConvoyDetail extends Convoy {
  formula?: { name: string; type: string; };
  notify?: string;
  workers: { agent: string; issue_id: string; age: string; }[];
  synthesis_ready: boolean;
  is_stranded: boolean;
  tracked_issues: TrackedIssueDetail[];
}

interface TrackedIssueDetail extends TrackedIssue {
  worker?: string;
  worker_age?: string;
  issue_type?: string;
  created_at?: string;
  blocked_by?: string[];
}
```

## Implementation
- Wrap gt convoy status --json for detail endpoint
- Wrap gt convoy stranded --json for stranded endpoint
- Add close convoy service function
- Parse synthesis readiness from convoy metadata
